This version includes a fix for a UI bug that affects some devices.

In this release we ve added the ability to create streaks. A streak is designed to keep track of a daily task. As you complete consecutive days your streak grows higher. There is an in app calendar to show every streak you ve completed on the corresponding day. Create as many streaks as you d like! We ve also implemented several new features and made a few improvements: Added ability to create streaks and manage streaks Added ability receive notifications for reminders Added privacy mode Added safety lock to prevent accidental changes to previous days Added ability to increase text size for more accessibility Minor graphical improvements Minor bug fixes and stability update
This version includes UI updates and minor bug fixes. Thanks for downloading!
